<title>USA: BFGoodrich names President David Burner CEO.</title>
<headline>BFGoodrich names President David Burner CEO.</headline>
<dateline>RICHFIELD, Ohio 1996-12-03</dateline>
<text>
<p>BFGoodrich Co said Tuesday that its board named company President David Burner to the additional position of chief executive officer.</p>
<p>John Ong, who has been chairman and chief executive since July 1, 1979, has relinquished the chief executive title but will remain chairman until he retires in 1997, the company said.</p>
<p>The company said Ong has chosen not to remain a company director after his retirement.</p>
